Parker got tired of his new toy.

47:48.120 --> 47:49.400
But that's kids.

47:50.320 --> 47:52.320
They're ingrates.

48:02.000 --> 48:02.960
[door slams]

48:03.920 --> 48:05.920
Monkey needs a hug.

48:07.000 --> 48:08.000
[Nish]  Whoa.

48:08.400 --> 48:11.720
Wait, so this is a crime museum.

48:11.800 --> 48:17.200
-Where's the crime in this?
-Well, the monkey is the crime.

48:17.280 --> 48:18.880
See, a couple of years back,

48:18.960 --> 48:21.000
