into limited formats like this.

48:25.320 --> 48:30.440
Gotta be able to express at least five
emotions for it to be humane, apparently.

48:30.520 --> 48:31.520
[chuckles]

48:31.600 --> 48:34.480
Human rights for cookies. Right, Carrie?

48:34.560 --> 48:36.560
Monkey needs a hug.

48:37.320 --> 48:38.480
She's still in there?

48:38.560 --> 48:40.920
