so, yeah.

48:41.000 --> 48:42.600
[chuckles] Go figure.

48:42.680 --> 48:46.000
Anyhow, ACLU raised one heck of a stink,

48:46.080 --> 48:49.480
and so thanks to this son of a monkey,
I was out on my ass from TCKR.

48:49.560 --> 48:51.400
Not even a severance package.

48:52.040 --> 48:54.200
It's why I started this place.

48:54.960 --> 48:59.200
