the moment he got locked up.

52:33.760 --> 52:35.160
I know, right?

52:35.240 --> 52:39.480
-Jesus Christ, Clay, it's your soul.
-Ain't no such thing.

52:40.360 --> 52:42.680
It's just a computer simulation
or somethin'.

52:42.760 --> 52:45.120
Then why does he need your permission?

52:45.880 --> 52:49.560
If my pardon comes through,
it won't matter.

52:51.240 --> 52:52.560
