this is gonna pay.

52:56.320 --> 53:00.800
It's gonna keep you and the kids
above water, maintain a roof over y'all.

53:00.880 --> 53:02.000
Baby, don't.

53:03.480 --> 53:05.120
This could be a good thing.

53:08.480 --> 53:10.280
But he never did get that pardon.

53:10.360 --> 53:12.880
Shit, no, 'cause he was guilty.

53:12.960 --> 53:15.800
