Just hang on in there.

55:30.400 --> 55:31.360
[Clayton gasps]

55:31.640 --> 55:32.840
What the fuck?

55:33.560 --> 55:38.280
See, I knew just seeing the guy
walking around captive, that was good,

55:38.360 --> 55:40.360
