55:40.440 --> 55:42.480
But pulling the lever yourself?

55:43.880 --> 55:45.560
Now, that's an attraction.

55:46.880 --> 55:48.440
-Hey!
-OK.

55:48.520 --> 55:50.640
-Hey!
