59:21.760 --> 59:22.800
[screams]

59:23.400 --> 59:25.760
[Nish]  Loners. Sadists.

59:26.560 --> 59:28.680
The supremacist sicko demographic.

59:30.200 --> 59:32.040
No, no, no, no, no, no, no. Out, out, out.

59:32.120 --> 59:34.120
[screaming, gasps]

59:35.000 --> 59:37.000
